Step 1
Make sure you have a developer product for sale.

Step 2
Create a Screen GUI to you game and add it to the Starter GUI folder. Then add a text button to the Screen GUI.

Step 3
Add regular script to the Screen GUI and paste in this code. (Make sure to change the "YourIDHere" to your developer product ID)


local id = YourIDHere

script.Parent.TextButton.MouseButton1Click:connect(function()
    game.MarketplaceService:PromptProductPurchase(script.Parent.Parent.Parent, id)
end)
